Revision history for App-Pod2Epub

0.04 August 24 2010

    ! Increased Pod::Simple dependency to 3.06 to ensure access to
      Pod::Simple::XHTML.


0.03 August 20 2010

    + Added option for adding an eBook cover image.

    ! The -c|-css option has changed to -s|--stylesheet.
      The -c option is now used for cover.


0.02 August 19 2010

    + Converted to EBook::EPUB 0.5 API.


0.01 August 18 2010

    + Initial CPAN release.

